{
  "stem": "734.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, after the war is over, we are free.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You should do away, you should do away with this word, prisoners.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are not prisoners.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are free then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What, what I was doing at the time was simply helping to get people who had intentions of going to Palestine, survivors who lived in Austria or Germany.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Especially, I was interested in getting people out of Austria to Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then eventually, I helped to get people from Germany to France.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that they could get closer to the ports of embarkation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, Marseilles, or from France was easier for them to get to Italy, maybe, whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there was a big-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] there was a big concentration of survivors in France, who were being shipped to Palestine illegally.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You realize this was a time when the British blockaded the, the Mediterranean.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To get through was not easy on a boat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, there were times they would [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] stop a boat with illegal immigrants.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would take them to Cyprus and keep them in internment camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was a rough time a lot of those people had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These camps are not much better from the camps the Germans had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, in some sense.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were not killing them, but they were really mistreating them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I did some of that, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, I have some good contacts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When I lived in Germany, I got to know some officers of the French Air Force, in an occupied part of Germany by France, around Friedrichshafen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I got to know some very incredible people, who were willing to help the [NON-ENGLISH], to help people emigrate to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
